title: 'Boys and Girl - Coronavirus Disruption; Dak Tag; Amari's Deal; Gerald McCoy, Free Agency Outlook
itunes:title: 'Boys and Girl - Coronavirus Disruption; Dak Tag; Amari's Deal; Gerald McCoy, Free Agency Outlook
description:
On today’s episode of the 'Boys and Girl Podcast, Jane and Bobby recap the first few days of free agency for the Cowboys, and discuss some of the ways the COVID-19 pandemic has had on NFL operations. Follow Jane and Bobby on Twitter and subscribe to get all the latest inside information from two of the most connected people in the Cowboys’ community.
